THE EVIL SPIRIT GROWS STRONGER

1120
00:41:42,416 --> 00:41:43,750
This is terrifying.

1121
00:41:43,751 --> 00:41:44,959
Let's row together.

1122
00:41:44,960 --> 00:41:46,294
- All together now.
- One.

1123
00:41:46,295 --> 00:41:47,588
One.

1124
00:41:48,172 --> 00:41:49,172
One.

1125
00:41:49,173 --> 00:41:51,342
ROWING TOGETHER UNDER YONG-JIN'S COMMAND

1126
00:41:51,967 --> 00:41:53,051
One.

